16
00:03:32,098 --> 00:03:33,059
Mira.

17
00:03:37,565 --> 00:03:39,961
¿Entonces vas a convertirte
al budismo?

18
00:03:40,825 --> 00:03:41,782
No.

19
00:03:42,071 --> 00:03:46,098
